# The act of [[dispel]]ling (''e.g.'' [[myth]]s, [[rumor]]s, [[magic]]), the state of being dispelled.
#:''The [[dispulsion]] of rumors is a difficult process.''
# Negative [[propulsion]], the act of reducing the effect of propulsion, the act of [[decelerate|decelerating]].
#:''A braking system is used for the [[dispulsion]] of a motor vehicle.''

